name: OMNIBUS PRIME
description:
I decided to sell my old piece to celebrate HEN500K.
..
This work is a form of criticism of the "Omnibus Law" policy by
Indonesian House of Representatives in year of 2020.
..
Composition of works ranging from characters, buildings, colors and other elements of this work is my perspective interpretation of the current condition.
..
All of the words are written in Indonesian tho.
..
